### Get Instagram Sync Status (Success)
# Returns: { pending: N, failed: N, failures: [...] }
# - pending: messages waiting in queue
# - failed: messages archived with failure reason
# - failures: array of { msg_id, url, failure_reason, failed_at }
GET {{$dotenv API_BASE_URL}}/instagram/sync/status
Authorization: Bearer {{$dotenv USER_TOKEN}}

### Auth Error - No Token
# Expected: 401 Unauthorized
GET {{$dotenv API_BASE_URL}}/instagram/sync/status
